{"tid":2246111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望我們係經歷緊第四波民主化","createTime":"2020-10-16T19:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T16:32:29.000Z","uid":210495,"like":48,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0da21cd11e56cfb30718a2abd3846c639e3fffc1","tid":2246111,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T19:00:12.000Z","msg":"利申：冇讀歷史 純粹呢幾年聽同睇多左知道咩係民主化浪潮<br />\n<br />\n孫中山：「民主自由是世界潮流，浩浩蕩蕩，順之者昌，逆之者亡。」<br />\n<br />\n第一次民主化長波：1828年－1926年（起源於美國革命和法國革命）<br />\n第二次民主化短波：1943年－1962年（始於第二次世界大戰，包括非殖民化後的新民主國家）<br />\n第三波民主化：1974年－1992年（始於1974年、1975年葡萄牙、希臘、西班牙的革命，終於東歐劇變）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第田波民主化：<br />\n大約2012年開始<br />\n阿拉伯之春<br />\n台灣（太陽花反服貿<br />\n香港（雨傘革命、流水革命<br />\n吉爾吉斯（總統下台東<br />\n泰國（反王室抗爭<br />\n<br />\n#StandWithThailand<br />\n#MilkTeaAlliance<br />\n#policebrutality<br />\n#whatishappeninginthailand"},{"pid":"0aaed271861a84faf82f1cfff06b7635c74001b4","tid":2246111,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T19:01:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"759448e2e060149075ac53a628f3aa68bb4ec50d","tid":2246111,"uid":347130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T19:02:50.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"44f61e12b72737989b5864624c481ef8c2027662","tid":2246111,"uid":206594,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T19:03:00.000Z","msg":"仲有白羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d988cd81f6159314a4a800a909afcaf303741d43","tid":2246111,"uid":347130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T19:03:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6de0f19e744d228f4c4b84193fe3fc17428575a","tid":2246111,"uid":210495,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44f61e12b72737989b5864624c481ef8c2027662","tid":2246111,"uid":206594,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T19:03:00.000Z","msg":"仲有白羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-1